  "title": "Induced Mutation for higher yield in Groundnut(Arachis hypogae)",
  "abstract": "An experiment was conducted during 1987-91 to induced polygenic variability for yield and its components in groundnut(Arachis Hypogae L.) Cultivation The seed of 'Jl 24' and 'KRG 1' groundnut were treated with 30 and 40kR does of gamma rays. The irrigated population showed significantly higher variability...........",
